1065
00:31:56,440 --> 00:31:59,200
[SPEAKER_01] i u pravoslavni hram da se pomolim.

1066
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:01,160
[SPEAKER_01] Isto tako imao sam susrete

1067
00:32:01,160 --> 00:32:02,140
[SPEAKER_01] i sa hođama,

1068
00:32:02,140 --> 00:32:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] sa efendijama.

1069
00:32:03,880 --> 00:32:05,420
[SPEAKER_01] Bogu hvala,

1070
00:32:05,420 --> 00:32:07,119
[SPEAKER_01] ovaj križ oprosta su blagoslovila

1071
00:32:07,119 --> 00:32:09,440
[SPEAKER_01] i sva tri aktivna biskupa u Bosni i Hercegovini

1072
00:32:09,440 --> 00:32:11,059
[SPEAKER_01] i kardinal Vinko Puljč,

1073
00:32:11,059 --> 00:32:12,619
[SPEAKER_01] koji me je vjenčao prije tri tjedna.

1074
00:32:12,619 --> 00:32:14,059
[SPEAKER_01] I Bogu hvala,

1075
00:32:14,059 --> 00:32:15,500
[SPEAKER_01] evo, imao sam susrete

1076
00:32:15,500 --> 00:32:17,960
[SPEAKER_01] i sa pravoslavnim sveštenicima,

1077
00:32:17,960 --> 00:32:19,700
[SPEAKER_01] i sa ljudima iz Srbije također.

1078
00:32:19,700 --> 00:32:20,880
[SPEAKER_01] I tu je bio jedan čovjek

1079
00:32:21,119 --> 00:32:22,480
[SPEAKER_01] u jednom hramu

1080
00:32:22,480 --> 00:32:23,640
[SPEAKER_01] koji održava taj hram.

1081
00:32:23,640 --> 00:32:25,380
[SPEAKER_01] On nije pravoslavni sveštenik,

1082
00:32:25,380 --> 00:32:26,559
[SPEAKER_01] ali održava hram.

1083
00:32:26,559 --> 00:32:27,619
[SPEAKER_01] Zove se Aleksa.

1084
00:32:27,619 --> 00:32:28,980
[SPEAKER_01] Prekrasan čovjek.

1085
00:32:28,980 --> 00:32:31,700
[SPEAKER_01] I dolazim ja sa svojim čačom.

1086
00:32:31,700 --> 00:32:33,720
[SPEAKER_01] Moj čača me tada pratio.

1087
00:32:33,720 --> 00:32:35,839
[SPEAKER_01] Nije tada niko zna za mene.

1088
00:32:35,839 --> 00:32:37,099
[SPEAKER_01] Čača krenuo sa mnom.

1089
00:32:37,099 --> 00:32:38,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znam se koji kralj.

1090
00:32:38,059 --> 00:32:38,920
[SPEAKER_01] Koji kralj.

1091
00:32:38,920 --> 00:32:42,319
[SPEAKER_01] I dolazimo mi u pravoslavni hram

1092
00:32:42,319 --> 00:32:43,420
[SPEAKER_01] i govoro ja o tom Aleksi.

1093
00:32:43,420 --> 00:32:45,759
[SPEAKER_01] Mogu li se ja pomoliti ovdje?

1094
00:32:45,759 --> 00:32:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] Govorio, on može.

1095
00:32:47,420 --> 00:32:48,519
[SPEAKER_01] Govorio ja,

1096
00:32:48,519 --> 00:32:50,319
[SPEAKER_01] ali prvo mi reci šta je se ovdje dogodilo.

1097
00:32:51,779 --> 00:32:52,539
[SPEAKER_01] Govorio, on.

1098
00:32:52,539 --> 00:32:55,660
[SPEAKER_01] Žao mi je što ti ovo moram reći,

1099
00:32:55,660 --> 00:32:56,079
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo.

1100
00:32:56,079 --> 00:32:57,839
[SPEAKER_01] Istina je takva.

1101
00:32:57,839 --> 00:33:00,099
[SPEAKER_01] Ovdje su Hrvati

1102
00:33:00,099 --> 00:33:02,400
[SPEAKER_01] ubili puno srpskog stanovništa.

1103
00:33:02,400 --> 00:33:04,380
[SPEAKER_01] Između ostalog i djece.

1104
00:33:04,380 --> 00:33:07,619
[SPEAKER_01] I meni ko Hrvatu stvarno

1105
00:33:07,619 --> 00:33:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] nije mi to bilo baš ugodno čuti.

1106
00:33:09,460 --> 00:33:11,400
[SPEAKER_01] Ali bilo je svega.

1107
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:14,559
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je svega sa sva tri naroda.

1108
00:33:14,559 --> 00:33:16,319
[SPEAKER_01] Negdje su Srbi ubili Hrvati,

1109
00:33:16,319 --> 00:33:17,460
[SPEAKER_01] negdje Hrvati Srbe.

1110
00:33:17,460 --> 00:33:18,460
[SPEAKER_01] Bilo je svega.

1111
00:33:18,460 --> 00:33:20,660
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam sad došao na takvo mjesto.

1112
00:33:21,599 --> 00:33:23,079
[SPEAKER_01] I stvarno mi nije to bilo ugodno čuti,

1113
00:33:23,079 --> 00:33:23,519
[SPEAKER_01] ali evo,

1114
00:33:23,519 --> 00:33:25,799
[SPEAKER_01] odlučio sam se poniziti

1115
00:33:25,799 --> 00:33:26,799
[SPEAKER_01] i zatražiti oprost.

1116
00:33:26,799 --> 00:33:28,380
[SPEAKER_01] I baš mi je došlo u srce

1117
00:33:28,380 --> 00:33:29,839
[SPEAKER_01] da Bog želi da kleknem

1118
00:33:29,839 --> 00:33:31,200
[SPEAKER_01] ispred ikone.

1119
00:33:31,200 --> 00:33:31,880
[SPEAKER_01] Evo,

1120
00:33:31,880 --> 00:33:33,039
[SPEAKER_01] kao ova ikona.

1121
00:33:33,039 --> 00:33:34,240
[SPEAKER_01] Baš zanimljivo.

1122
00:33:34,240 --> 00:33:34,720
[SPEAKER_01] Slična.

1123
00:33:35,640 --> 00:33:38,099
[SPEAKER_01] i došlo mi je da kažem ove riječi.

1124
00:33:38,099 --> 00:33:40,000
[SPEAKER_01] Oče nebeski,

1125
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:40,859
[SPEAKER_01] u ime Isusovo,

1126
00:33:40,859 --> 00:33:42,640
[SPEAKER_01] po sili i snazi Duha Svetoga,

1127
00:33:42,640 --> 00:33:45,319
[SPEAKER_01] ja kao pojedinac iz Hrvatskog naroda

1128
00:33:45,319 --> 00:33:47,559
[SPEAKER_01] se kajem za sve one zločine

1129
00:33:47,559 --> 00:33:50,119
[SPEAKER_01] koje su pojedinci u Hrvatskom narodu

1130
00:33:50,119 --> 00:33:52,380
[SPEAKER_01] učinili srpskom stanovništvu.

1131
00:33:52,920 --> 00:33:54,319
[SPEAKER_01] I molim za oprost.

1132
00:33:54,319 --> 00:33:58,980
[SPEAKER_01] I kad sam ja to izgovorio,

1133
00:33:58,980 --> 00:34:02,619
[SPEAKER_01] taj čovjek je bio baš sretan.

1134
00:34:02,619 --> 00:34:04,440
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je radostan.

1135
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:06,839
[SPEAKER_01] On to možda nije neočekivo.

1136
00:34:06,839 --> 00:34:09,280
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazi čovjek sa križem od metar,

1137
00:34:09,280 --> 00:34:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] prvi puga vidi u životu,

1138
00:34:11,000 --> 00:34:13,360
[SPEAKER_01] a možda sam ja i prvi Hrvat

1139
00:34:13,360 --> 00:34:14,900
[SPEAKER_01] koji je tu došao,

1140
00:34:14,900 --> 00:34:17,260
[SPEAKER_01] pokajo se, ponizio

1141
00:34:17,260 --> 00:34:18,239
[SPEAKER_01] i zatraži oprost.

1142
00:34:18,239 --> 00:34:20,420
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerujte mi,

1143
00:34:20,420 --> 00:34:21,860
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam vidio na njemu

1144
00:34:21,860 --> 00:34:24,559
[SPEAKER_01] da je se u njemu dogodilo jedno ozdravljenje,

1145
00:34:24,559 --> 00:34:25,599
[SPEAKER_01] a i u meni isto.

1146
00:34:25,599 --> 00:34:28,780
[SPEAKER_01] Jer čita život mi se predstavljaju drugi

1147
00:34:28,780 --> 00:34:30,300
[SPEAKER_01] kao neka opasnost,

1148
00:34:30,300 --> 00:34:32,340
[SPEAKER_01] a svi smo ljubljena djeca Božja.

1149
00:34:32,340 --> 00:34:35,039
[SPEAKER_01] I nakon toga on dolazi do mene i kaže

1150
00:34:35,039 --> 00:34:37,139
[SPEAKER_01] Jospe, hvala ti puno za molitvu,

1151
00:34:37,139 --> 00:34:38,719
[SPEAKER_01] vidi se da je iz srca.

1152
00:34:38,719 --> 00:34:41,639
[SPEAKER_01] Molim te, kad završi križni put,

1153
00:34:41,639 --> 00:34:42,719
[SPEAKER_01] dođi opet.

1154
00:34:42,719 --> 00:34:44,599
[SPEAKER_01] I ja zagrli njega,

1155
00:34:44,599 --> 00:34:45,539
[SPEAKER_01] on mene.

1156
00:34:45,539 --> 00:34:47,980
[SPEAKER_01] I tu je se dogodilo jedno ozdravljenje

1157
00:34:47,980 --> 00:34:50,760
[SPEAKER_01] i pomerenje između Hrvata i Srbina.

1158
00:34:50,800 --> 00:34:53,780
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je bio presretan.

1159
00:34:53,780 --> 00:34:56,960
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je tada bio presretan,

1160
00:34:56,960 --> 00:34:59,539
[SPEAKER_01] jer upravo on to želi u Bosni i Hercegovini.

1161
00:34:59,539 --> 00:35:00,619
[SPEAKER_01] Želi oprost.

1162
00:35:00,619 --> 00:35:03,260
[SPEAKER_01] Da je ovo bio križ provokacije,

1163
00:35:03,260 --> 00:35:04,539
[SPEAKER_01] vjerujte mi,

1164
00:35:04,539 --> 00:35:07,059
[SPEAKER_01] mene bi išamarali i jedni i drugi i treći.

1165
00:35:07,059 --> 00:35:10,239
[SPEAKER_01] Da je ovo bio križ provokacije,

1166
00:35:10,239 --> 00:35:12,460
[SPEAKER_01] ali pošto je ovo bio križ oprosta,

1167
00:35:12,460 --> 00:35:18,320
[SPEAKER_01] a najveća Božja osobina je upraštanje i najljepša,

1168
00:35:18,320 --> 00:35:22,260
[SPEAKER_01] tada je Bog pokorio zlo i otvorio svima srce.

1169
00:35:22,260 --> 00:35:26,860
[SPEAKER_01] Otvorio je srce i pravoslavcima i muslimanima i katolicima

1170
00:35:26,860 --> 00:35:30,239
[SPEAKER_01] da prihvate križ kao simbol pomirenja.

1171
00:35:33,320 --> 00:35:34,159
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerujte mi,

1172
00:35:34,159 --> 00:35:37,500
[SPEAKER_01] kada sam vidio da se širi taj požar ljubavi,

1173
00:35:37,500 --> 00:35:40,579
[SPEAKER_01] kada sam vidio da gdje god dođem sa križem,

1174
00:35:40,579 --> 00:35:41,980
[SPEAKER_01] da je križ dobro došao,

1175
00:35:41,980 --> 00:35:44,360
[SPEAKER_01] da je prihvaćen i da ima silu i snagu,

1176
00:35:44,360 --> 00:35:45,960
[SPEAKER_01] baš sam bio radostan.

1177
00:35:46,179 --> 00:35:47,340
[SPEAKER_01] Sjećam se u jednom trenutku,

1178
00:35:47,340 --> 00:35:49,679
[SPEAKER_01] dolazi jedna muslimanka u Sarajevu

1179
00:35:49,679 --> 00:35:50,619
[SPEAKER_01] i pita me,

1180
00:35:50,619 --> 00:35:51,260
[SPEAKER_01] gdje ti je krst?

1181
00:35:51,260 --> 00:35:52,920
[SPEAKER_01] Gdje je krst?

1182
00:35:52,920 --> 00:35:56,039
[SPEAKER_01] A men taman tada došla obitelj

1183
00:35:56,039 --> 00:35:58,239
[SPEAKER_01] i ja ostavio križ malo kod obitelji.

1184
00:35:58,239 --> 00:35:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] I govori ona,

1185
00:35:59,960 --> 00:36:01,980
[SPEAKER_01] želim se uskat sa krstom.

1186
00:36:01,980 --> 00:36:03,880
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ja stvarno.

1187
00:36:03,880 --> 00:36:04,739
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ona,

1188
00:36:04,739 --> 00:36:06,480
[SPEAKER_01] da, želim se uskat sa krstom.

1189
00:36:06,480 --> 00:36:09,539
[SPEAKER_01] I ja donio križ.

1190
00:36:09,539 --> 00:36:12,119
[SPEAKER_01] Muslimanka stvarno,

1191
00:36:12,119 --> 00:36:12,320
[SPEAKER_01] evo,

1192
00:36:12,320 --> 00:36:13,519
[SPEAKER_01] bila je u hijabu,

1193
00:36:13,519 --> 00:36:15,260
[SPEAKER_01] baš otvorila je srce

1194
00:36:15,260 --> 00:36:17,320
[SPEAKER_01] za simbol pomirenje.

1195
00:36:17,320 --> 00:36:20,079
[SPEAKER_01] Dolazi također jedan musliman,

1196
00:36:20,079 --> 00:36:22,059
[SPEAKER_01] mrcina dva metra stoki

1197
00:36:22,059 --> 00:36:24,139
[SPEAKER_01] ili domene u jednom je gradu

1198
00:36:24,139 --> 00:36:24,840
[SPEAKER_01] i kaže,

1199
00:36:24,840 --> 00:36:25,320
[SPEAKER_01] Jospe,

1200
00:36:25,320 --> 00:36:26,639
[SPEAKER_01] ja imam samo jednu želju.

1201
00:36:26,639 --> 00:36:27,880
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ja koju?

1202
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:31,239
[SPEAKER_01] Koju želim se uskat sa krstom.

1203
00:36:31,239 --> 00:36:32,380
[SPEAKER_01] I on isto.

1204
00:36:32,380 --> 00:36:34,219
[SPEAKER_01] I kad sam vidio

1205
00:36:34,219 --> 00:36:36,280
[SPEAKER_01] da i predstavnici drugih religija

1206
00:36:36,280 --> 00:36:37,820
[SPEAKER_01] otvraju srce za ovaj križ,

1207
00:36:37,820 --> 00:36:40,500
[SPEAKER_01] znao sam da on ima posebnu snagu.

1208
00:36:40,500 --> 00:36:44,340
[SPEAKER_01] Ovaj križ je noslo preko tišću ljudi

1209
00:36:44,340 --> 00:36:45,760
[SPEAKER_01] kroz cijelu u Bosni i Hercegovini.

1210
00:36:45,760 --> 00:36:48,380
[SPEAKER_01] Poljubilo ga je preko 3-4 tisuće ljudi.

1211
00:36:48,380 --> 00:36:53,139
[SPEAKER_01] I stvarno je zapalio

1212
00:36:53,139 --> 00:36:55,820
[SPEAKER_01] jedan požar ljubavi u Bosni i Hercegovini.

1213
00:36:55,820 --> 00:36:57,219
[SPEAKER_01] I kada mi je Mišo rekao

1214
00:36:57,219 --> 00:36:58,619
[SPEAKER_01] da je sada duhovno stanje

1215
00:36:58,619 --> 00:36:59,800
[SPEAKER_01] u Bosni i Hercegovini

1216
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:01,360
[SPEAKER_01] mirnije i drugačije nego prije,

1217
00:37:01,360 --> 00:37:03,059
[SPEAKER_01] moram priznat da sam ponosan.

1218
00:37:03,059 --> 00:37:05,659
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam ja neki svetac,

1219
00:37:05,659 --> 00:37:08,420
[SPEAKER_01] nisam ja neki izabran posebno čovjek.

1220
00:37:08,760 --> 00:37:11,000
[SPEAKER_01] Vidjeli ste da sam se raspuo ovdje kad sam došao.

1221
00:37:11,000 --> 00:37:13,059
[SPEAKER_01] Znači raspuo sam se.

1222
00:37:13,059 --> 00:37:15,320
[SPEAKER_01] Ja sam običan čovjek.

1223
00:37:15,320 --> 00:37:19,059
[SPEAKER_01] Pun mana i slabosti.

1224
00:37:19,059 --> 00:37:19,800
[SPEAKER_01] Kao i svi mi.

1225
00:37:19,800 --> 00:37:22,179
[SPEAKER_01] Ali crkva je zajednica grešnika

1226
00:37:22,179 --> 00:37:24,039
[SPEAKER_01] i Bog poziva grešnike

1227
00:37:24,039 --> 00:37:26,260
[SPEAKER_01] da ga slijede.

1228
00:37:26,260 --> 00:37:29,940
[SPEAKER_01] Ja vjerujem da će Bog i danas

1229
00:37:29,940 --> 00:37:31,059
[SPEAKER_01] i da je jučer učinio

1230
00:37:31,059 --> 00:37:32,460
[SPEAKER_01] puno prekrasnih stvari

1231
00:37:32,460 --> 00:37:35,179
[SPEAKER_01] i dao mnoge plodove i pocaje u vašem srcu.

1232
00:37:35,179 --> 00:37:37,619
[SPEAKER_01] Ne mora svak uzeti doslovno križ

1233
00:37:37,619 --> 00:37:38,960
[SPEAKER_01] i nositi ga po svojoj zemlji.

1234
00:37:38,960 --> 00:37:40,659
[SPEAKER_01] Ako bude i takvi pocaje,

1235
00:37:40,659 --> 00:37:41,340
[SPEAKER_01] a Bogu hvala.

1236
00:37:41,340 --> 00:37:44,000
[SPEAKER_01] Evo, Jim je to osje doćeo prošle godine.

1237
00:37:44,000 --> 00:37:45,199
[SPEAKER_01] Meni je došlo.

1238
00:37:45,199 --> 00:37:47,179
[SPEAKER_01] Na kraju je bila Božja volja.

1239
00:37:47,179 --> 00:37:49,219
[SPEAKER_01] Da je meni rekao biskup,

1240
00:37:49,219 --> 00:37:50,280
[SPEAKER_01] Jospe, nemoj to rad.

1241
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:51,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ja bi bio poslušan.

1242
00:37:52,099 --> 00:37:53,460
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ja ne želim ovo rad

1243
00:37:53,460 --> 00:37:54,619
[SPEAKER_01] bez svoje crkve.

1244
00:37:54,619 --> 00:37:56,880
[SPEAKER_01] Ti ste zarčnik,

1245
00:37:56,880 --> 00:37:58,239
[SPEAKER_01] a crkva je zarčnica.

1246
00:37:58,239 --> 00:37:59,780
[SPEAKER_01] Dosta mi je devijacija.

1247
00:37:59,780 --> 00:38:02,340
[SPEAKER_01] Dosta mi je u životu lutanja.

1248
00:38:02,340 --> 00:38:04,559
[SPEAKER_01] Puno godina sam proveo

1249
00:38:04,559 --> 00:38:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] u teškom grijehu.

1250
00:38:05,480 --> 00:38:07,280
[SPEAKER_01] Želim stvarno biti ponizan

1251
00:38:07,280 --> 00:38:08,019
[SPEAKER_01] i poslušan

1252
00:38:08,019 --> 00:38:09,059
[SPEAKER_01] i u spratnju

1253
00:38:09,059 --> 00:38:10,559
[SPEAKER_01] i biskupa i duhovnika

1254
00:38:10,559 --> 00:38:12,079
[SPEAKER_01] slijediti Božje pocaje.

1255
00:38:12,079 --> 00:38:14,440
[SPEAKER_01] Jako je bitna ta poslušnost

1256
00:38:14,440 --> 00:38:15,699
[SPEAKER_01] i zajedništvo sa crkvom.

1257
00:38:15,699 --> 00:38:17,019
[SPEAKER_01] I Bogu hvala

1258
00:38:17,019 --> 00:38:18,179
[SPEAKER_01] na našim svećenicima.

1259
00:38:18,179 --> 00:38:21,360
[SPEAKER_01] Sad ću vam reći par neki smiješnih scena.

1260
00:38:21,699 --> 00:38:22,400
[SPEAKER_01] da ne bi zaspali.

1261
00:38:22,400 --> 00:38:25,559
[SPEAKER_01] Kad sam došao u jedno mjesto

1262
00:38:25,559 --> 00:38:26,599
[SPEAKER_01] u Bosni i Hercegovini,

1263
00:38:26,599 --> 00:38:29,260
[SPEAKER_01] dolazi jedna romkinja do mene

1264
00:38:29,260 --> 00:38:31,539
[SPEAKER_01] i kaže

1265
00:38:31,539 --> 00:38:33,260
[SPEAKER_01] Ćao ba,

1266
00:38:33,260 --> 00:38:34,340
[SPEAKER_01] pretinite na TikToku.

1267
00:38:36,980 --> 00:38:37,800
[SPEAKER_01] govori ja stvarno.

1268
00:38:37,800 --> 00:38:38,980
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ona je,

1269
00:38:38,980 --> 00:38:39,780
[SPEAKER_01] jebla, dobar si.

1270
00:38:39,780 --> 00:38:41,699
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ja, hvala ti.

1271
00:38:41,699 --> 00:38:42,679
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ona,

1272
00:38:42,679 --> 00:38:43,619
[SPEAKER_01] jebla, zapratim,

1273
00:38:43,619 --> 00:38:44,380
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam Bosanka.

1274
00:38:44,380 --> 00:38:47,619
[SPEAKER_01] U Brčko mi došli,

1275
00:38:47,619 --> 00:38:49,000
[SPEAKER_01] ja i Matija,

1276
00:38:49,000 --> 00:38:49,659
[SPEAKER_01] svega ovdje,

1277
00:38:49,659 --> 00:38:50,820
[SPEAKER_01] prekrasan čovjek,

1278
00:38:50,820 --> 00:38:52,360
[SPEAKER_01] drago mi je da je tu s nama.

1279
00:38:52,900 --> 00:38:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] došli mi u Brčko

1280
00:38:53,800 --> 00:38:56,320
[SPEAKER_01] i sada šetamo kroz centar

1281
00:38:56,320 --> 00:38:58,340
[SPEAKER_01] i dva Roma,

1282
00:38:58,340 --> 00:38:59,960
[SPEAKER_01] možda četrnec godina.

1283
00:38:59,960 --> 00:39:01,699
[SPEAKER_01] Dolaze do nas

1284
00:39:01,699 --> 00:39:03,599
[SPEAKER_01] i motaju se oko križa.

1285
00:39:03,599 --> 00:39:06,119
[SPEAKER_01] Dva Roma od četrnec godina.

1286
00:39:06,599 --> 00:39:08,079
[SPEAKER_01] i vidi ja gledaj oni u križ.

1287
00:39:08,079 --> 00:39:09,380
[SPEAKER_01] I govori ja,

1288
00:39:09,380 --> 00:39:10,320
[SPEAKER_01] je li vam fin križ?

1289
00:39:10,320 --> 00:39:12,360
[SPEAKER_01] Gleda ovaj jedan,

1290
00:39:12,360 --> 00:39:14,400
[SPEAKER_01] gleda,

1291
00:39:14,400 --> 00:39:15,340
[SPEAKER_01] gleda,

1292
00:39:15,340 --> 00:39:17,059
[SPEAKER_01] vidi ode Isusa,

1293
00:39:17,059 --> 00:39:17,980
[SPEAKER_01] šta će Isusa ode,

1294
00:39:17,980 --> 00:39:18,860
[SPEAKER_01] jadan apačen,

1295
00:39:18,860 --> 00:39:21,320
[SPEAKER_01] satran od bolova.

1296
00:39:21,320 --> 00:39:23,519
[SPEAKER_00] Gleda ga on,

1297
00:39:23,519 --> 00:39:24,159
[SPEAKER_00] gleda,

1298
00:39:24,159 --> 00:39:24,820
[SPEAKER_00] gleda,

1299
00:39:24,820 --> 00:39:25,380
[SPEAKER_00] gleda

1300
00:39:25,380 --> 00:39:26,059
[SPEAKER_00] i kaže

1301
00:39:26,059 --> 00:39:28,780
[SPEAKER_00] je smršo.

1302
00:39:36,599 --> 00:39:38,699
[SPEAKER_01] dolazi ja u Jablancu,

1303
00:39:38,699 --> 00:39:40,480
[SPEAKER_01] staje neki džip,

1304
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:41,840
[SPEAKER_01] mrcna neka,

1305
