[SPEAKER_01] stok ili brada,

1306
00:39:43,300 --> 00:39:45,119
[SPEAKER_01] zlatni lančić oko vrata,

1307
00:39:45,119 --> 00:39:47,639
[SPEAKER_01] otvara prozor,

1308
00:39:47,639 --> 00:39:49,019
[SPEAKER_01] ja kontak gotovo,

1309
00:39:49,019 --> 00:39:49,980
[SPEAKER_01] evo nisu me,

1310
00:39:49,980 --> 00:39:52,059
[SPEAKER_01] nisu me riješili u Mostaru,

1311
00:39:52,059 --> 00:39:53,119
[SPEAKER_01] riješi me u Jablancu.

1312
00:39:53,119 --> 00:39:55,539
[SPEAKER_01] Ali prekrasan čovjek na kraju,

1313
00:39:55,539 --> 00:39:58,199
[SPEAKER_01] kako je loša imat neke predrasude.

1314
00:39:58,199 --> 00:40:00,860
[SPEAKER_01] Otvara on prozor od džipa

1315
00:40:00,860 --> 00:40:01,420
[SPEAKER_01] i kaže

1316
00:40:01,420 --> 00:40:02,440
[SPEAKER_01] Jospe,

1317
00:40:02,440 --> 00:40:04,420
[SPEAKER_01] bošnjak musliman,

1318
00:40:04,420 --> 00:40:06,199
[SPEAKER_01] govori ja rec prijatelju,

1319
00:40:06,599 --> 00:40:07,239
[SPEAKER_01] govori ja on,

1320
00:40:07,239 --> 00:40:09,980
[SPEAKER_01] dira li teko?

1321
00:40:09,980 --> 00:40:15,940
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ja nije,

1322
00:40:15,940 --> 00:40:16,219
[SPEAKER_01] brat,

1323
00:40:16,219 --> 00:40:18,539
[SPEAKER_01] ali me šini da bi ti mogo.

1324
00:40:18,539 --> 00:40:21,820
[SPEAKER_01] Nisam to rekao,

1325
00:40:21,820 --> 00:40:22,739
[SPEAKER_01] ali to sam razmišljao.

1326
00:40:22,739 --> 00:40:24,960
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ja on,

1327
00:40:24,960 --> 00:40:25,420
[SPEAKER_01] slušaj,

1328
00:40:25,420 --> 00:40:27,219
[SPEAKER_01] ako te neko bude dira,

1329
00:40:27,219 --> 00:40:29,119
[SPEAKER_01] sami javi.

1330
00:40:29,119 --> 00:40:31,800
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ja dobro.

1331
00:40:31,800 --> 00:40:32,699
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ja on,

1332
00:40:32,699 --> 00:40:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] piš broj.

1333
00:40:36,599 --> 00:40:38,260
[SPEAKER_01] ja mislim da ga isam,

1334
00:40:38,260 --> 00:40:39,079
[SPEAKER_01] možda imam na niku.

1335
00:40:39,079 --> 00:40:41,320
[SPEAKER_01] I zapisao ja broj,

1336
00:40:41,320 --> 00:40:41,960
[SPEAKER_01] govori ja dobro,

1337
00:40:41,960 --> 00:40:42,980
[SPEAKER_01] kako ću pisat?

1338
00:40:42,980 --> 00:40:43,460
[SPEAKER_01] Govori je on,

1339
00:40:43,460 --> 00:40:45,340
[SPEAKER_01] Sancho.

1340
00:40:45,340 --> 00:40:48,699
[SPEAKER_01] Sancho.

1341
00:40:48,699 --> 00:40:50,260
[SPEAKER_01] Hvala Sanchi,

1342
00:40:50,260 --> 00:40:51,079
[SPEAKER_01] Boga blagoslovio.

1343
00:40:51,079 --> 00:40:53,280
[SPEAKER_01] Što se brine za mene.

1344
00:40:53,280 --> 00:40:56,280
[SPEAKER_01] I bila jedna scena

1345
00:40:56,280 --> 00:40:58,320
[SPEAKER_01] u jednom gradu

1346
00:40:58,320 --> 00:40:59,340
[SPEAKER_01] u Bosni i Hercegovini,

1347
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:04,780
[SPEAKER_01] gdje je jedan momak

1348
00:41:04,780 --> 00:41:06,000
[SPEAKER_01] psovo na mene.

1349
00:41:06,000 --> 00:41:08,099
[SPEAKER_01] Psovo na mene

1350
00:41:08,099 --> 00:41:10,099
[SPEAKER_01] i baš je onako bio ljut.

1351
00:41:10,099 --> 00:41:11,500
[SPEAKER_01] Ali taj momak,

1352
00:41:11,500 --> 00:41:12,000
[SPEAKER_01] vidi se,

1353
00:41:12,000 --> 00:41:13,579
[SPEAKER_01] ima oko 17-18 godina,

1354
00:41:13,579 --> 00:41:14,800
[SPEAKER_01] dečkoj u pubertetu.

1355
00:41:14,800 --> 00:41:19,119
[SPEAKER_01] I kada su to vidjeli ljudi

1356
00:41:19,119 --> 00:41:19,920
[SPEAKER_01] oko njega,

1357
00:41:19,920 --> 00:41:21,480
[SPEAKER_01] ljudi u tom gradu,

1358
00:41:21,480 --> 00:41:24,719
[SPEAKER_01] nisu to mogli vjerovat.

1359
00:41:25,340 --> 00:41:26,820
[SPEAKER_01] da psuje na mene,

1360
00:41:26,820 --> 00:41:27,960
[SPEAKER_01] a nosim križ

1361
00:41:27,960 --> 00:41:28,820
[SPEAKER_01] kroz njihov grad.

1362
00:41:28,820 --> 00:41:30,760
[SPEAKER_01] A tada se već proširila priča

1363
00:41:30,760 --> 00:41:31,739
[SPEAKER_01] da dolazim u miru.

1364
00:41:31,739 --> 00:41:34,179
[SPEAKER_01] I to su vidjela tri momka

1365
00:41:34,179 --> 00:41:36,860
[SPEAKER_01] od možda 30 godina.

1366
00:41:36,860 --> 00:41:39,420
[SPEAKER_01] I ništa ja sam to zanemario.

1367
00:41:39,420 --> 00:41:41,079
[SPEAKER_01] Znao sam ja da bi moglo bit

1368
00:41:41,079 --> 00:41:42,659
[SPEAKER_01] nekih određenih komentara

1369
00:41:42,659 --> 00:41:43,920
[SPEAKER_01] i tako.

1370
00:41:43,920 --> 00:41:45,619
[SPEAKER_01] Iako stvarno ih nije bilo puno.

1371
00:41:45,619 --> 00:41:46,559
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerujte mi,

1372
00:41:46,559 --> 00:41:49,019
[SPEAKER_01] od deset tišća susreta s ljudima.

1373
00:41:49,019 --> 00:41:50,500
[SPEAKER_01] Imao sam možda pet

1374
00:41:50,500 --> 00:41:51,800
[SPEAKER_01] neugodnih iskustava.

1375
00:41:51,800 --> 00:41:53,800
[SPEAKER_01] I to je bilo ono,

1376
00:41:53,800 --> 00:41:54,920
[SPEAKER_01] vidi budale.

1377
00:41:55,340 --> 00:41:57,079
[SPEAKER_01] Brate, to bi mi možda rekli

1378
00:41:57,079 --> 00:41:57,960
[SPEAKER_01] i moji.

1379
00:41:57,960 --> 00:42:03,280
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ono, nije baš običajeno

1380
00:42:03,280 --> 00:42:04,300
[SPEAKER_01] da nosiš križ

1381
00:42:04,300 --> 00:42:06,079
[SPEAKER_01] kroz Bosnu i Hercegonu.

1382
00:42:06,079 --> 00:42:06,920
[SPEAKER_01] Iako naravno,

1383
00:42:06,920 --> 00:42:08,940
[SPEAKER_01] moja biter me stvarno podržala

1384
00:42:08,940 --> 00:42:10,460
[SPEAKER_01] i zahvalan sam im neizmjerno.

1385
00:42:10,460 --> 00:42:11,639
[SPEAKER_01] I ponosni su sada

1386
00:42:11,639 --> 00:42:12,980
[SPEAKER_01] i evo, Bogu hvala na tome.

1387
00:42:12,980 --> 00:42:14,599
[SPEAKER_01] Ali zanimljivost je

1388
00:42:14,599 --> 00:42:16,539
[SPEAKER_01] kada je taj dečko psovo na mene,

1389
00:42:16,539 --> 00:42:20,360
[SPEAKER_01] ja sam otišao u samostan,

1390
00:42:20,360 --> 00:42:21,440
[SPEAKER_01] tu večer sam spavao

1391
00:42:21,440 --> 00:42:23,280
[SPEAKER_01] kod jednog afratra u samostanu

1392
00:42:23,280 --> 00:42:24,980
[SPEAKER_01] i nakon sada vremena

1393
00:42:24,980 --> 00:42:26,380
[SPEAKER_01] dolaze tri momka,

1394
00:42:26,380 --> 00:42:27,000
[SPEAKER_01] kucaju,

1395
00:42:27,000 --> 00:42:28,599
[SPEAKER_01] kucaju

1396
00:42:28,599 --> 00:42:30,260
[SPEAKER_01] na vrata samostana

1397
00:42:30,260 --> 00:42:31,840
[SPEAKER_01] i traže Jospa.

1398
00:42:31,840 --> 00:42:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] Ja izlazim

1399
00:42:33,519 --> 00:42:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] i govore oni meni.

1400
00:42:34,980 --> 00:42:36,719
[SPEAKER_01] Kaže, Jospe, oprosti,

1401
00:42:36,719 --> 00:42:38,719
[SPEAKER_01] ovo nije prava slika

1402
00:42:38,719 --> 00:42:39,619
[SPEAKER_01] našeg grada.

1403
00:42:39,619 --> 00:42:41,659
[SPEAKER_01] Oprosti nam puno.

1404
00:42:41,659 --> 00:42:43,780
[SPEAKER_01] Tri momka od 30 godina

1405
00:42:43,780 --> 00:42:45,400
[SPEAKER_01] dolaze u poniznosti,

1406
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:46,039
[SPEAKER_01] raskajani

1407
00:42:46,039 --> 00:42:46,800
[SPEAKER_01] i kaže,

1408
00:42:46,800 --> 00:42:47,940
[SPEAKER_01] ovo nije prava slika

1409
00:42:47,940 --> 00:42:48,800
[SPEAKER_01] našeg grada,

1410
00:42:48,800 --> 00:42:50,300
[SPEAKER_01] ti si ovdje dobrodošao.

1411
00:42:50,860 --> 00:42:53,039
[SPEAKER_01] Vjerujte me da ta njihova poniznost

1412
00:42:53,039 --> 00:42:54,719
[SPEAKER_01] i to njihovo zajedništo

1413
00:42:54,719 --> 00:42:55,519
[SPEAKER_01] u poniznosti

1414
00:42:55,519 --> 00:42:56,940
[SPEAKER_01] me je toliko dodirnulo

1415
00:42:56,940 --> 00:42:58,159
[SPEAKER_01] da sam bio oduševljen.

1416
00:42:58,159 --> 00:43:00,039
[SPEAKER_01] Bog je blagoslovio.

1417
00:43:00,039 --> 00:43:02,440
[SPEAKER_01] Nakon toga je oslijedio

1418
00:43:02,440 --> 00:43:03,679
[SPEAKER_01] zenički zatvor.

1419
00:43:03,679 --> 00:43:05,480
[SPEAKER_01] Baš sam imao želju

1420
00:43:05,480 --> 00:43:06,980
[SPEAKER_01] da odem u zenički zatvor.

1421
00:43:08,139 --> 00:43:09,280
[SPEAKER_01] Dobro, ovo sam malo zvuči.

1422
00:43:09,280 --> 00:43:11,860
[SPEAKER_01] Malo zvuči.

1423
00:43:11,860 --> 00:43:13,039
[SPEAKER_01] Nemojte doslovno sveti.

1424
00:43:13,039 --> 00:43:14,840
[SPEAKER_01] Uglavnom imao sam želju

1425
00:43:14,840 --> 00:43:16,300
[SPEAKER_01] da posjetim zatvorenike.

1426
00:43:16,300 --> 00:43:19,360
[SPEAKER_01] Znam da Isus ima posebno

1427
00:43:19,360 --> 00:43:21,599
[SPEAKER_01] milosrđe za ljude

1428
00:43:21,599 --> 00:43:22,940
[SPEAKER_01] koji su posebno ranjeni.

1429
00:43:22,940 --> 00:43:25,420
[SPEAKER_01] A kada neko učini

1430
00:43:25,420 --> 00:43:26,539
[SPEAKER_01] neko veliko zlo,

1431
00:43:26,539 --> 00:43:28,539
[SPEAKER_01] često to bude plod

1432
00:43:28,539 --> 00:43:29,840
[SPEAKER_01] duboke ranjenosti

1433
00:43:29,840 --> 00:43:31,719
[SPEAKER_01] koju su ti ljudi

1434
00:43:31,719 --> 00:43:32,900
[SPEAKER_01] doživjeli u djetinstvu.

1435
00:43:32,900 --> 00:43:35,500
[SPEAKER_01] I baš sam nekako htio

1436
00:43:35,500 --> 00:43:37,079
[SPEAKER_01] da im Bog iskaže milosrđe.

1437
00:43:37,860 --> 00:43:38,500
[SPEAKER_01] I Bogu hvala,

1438
00:43:38,500 --> 00:43:39,260
[SPEAKER_01] Bog mi je providio

1439
00:43:39,260 --> 00:43:40,679
[SPEAKER_01] preko jednog divnog svećenika

1440
00:43:40,679 --> 00:43:41,300
[SPEAKER_01] u Zenci

1441
00:43:41,300 --> 00:43:43,360
[SPEAKER_01] da dođem do zatvorenika

1442
00:43:43,360 --> 00:43:45,000
[SPEAKER_01] i imali smo jedan susret.

1443
00:43:45,000 --> 00:43:46,340
[SPEAKER_01] I to je bilo prekrasno.

1444
00:43:46,340 --> 00:43:48,039
[SPEAKER_01] Bio je katolički svećenik,

1445
00:43:48,039 --> 00:43:49,460
[SPEAKER_01] bio je hođa

1446
00:43:49,460 --> 00:43:51,239
[SPEAKER_01] i bio je pravoslavni sveštenik.

1447
00:43:51,239 --> 00:43:52,440
[SPEAKER_01] I ja.

1448
00:43:52,440 --> 00:43:54,599
[SPEAKER_01] I naravno direktor zatvora

1449
00:43:54,599 --> 00:43:55,460
[SPEAKER_01] i ostali ljudi.

1450
00:43:55,460 --> 00:43:56,940
[SPEAKER_01] I sad je tu došlo

1451
00:43:56,940 --> 00:43:58,320
[SPEAKER_01] trice zatvorenika.

1452
00:43:58,320 --> 00:44:00,559
[SPEAKER_01] Baš su bili onako izmješani

1453
00:44:00,559 --> 00:44:02,340
[SPEAKER_01] bošnjaci, Srbiji i Hrvati.

1454
00:44:02,340 --> 00:44:04,340
[SPEAKER_01] I oni su se sad poredali

1455
00:44:04,340 --> 00:44:06,719
[SPEAKER_01] ispred mene

1456
00:44:06,719 --> 00:44:07,579
[SPEAKER_01] i meni je rekao direktor

1457
00:44:07,579 --> 00:44:08,239
[SPEAKER_01] zatvora.

1458
00:44:08,239 --> 00:44:09,719
[SPEAKER_01] Jospe, imaš 15 minuta.

1459
00:44:09,719 --> 00:44:11,139
[SPEAKER_01] Govori ja, dobro.

1460
00:44:11,139 --> 00:44:12,760
[SPEAKER_01] I meni je došlo srce

1461
00:44:12,760 --> 00:44:14,019
[SPEAKER_01] da Isus želi samo ovo.

1462
00:44:14,019 --> 00:44:15,420
[SPEAKER_01] Da je im pričan

1463
00:44:15,420 --> 00:44:16,440
[SPEAKER_01] o milosrđu.

1464
00:44:16,440 --> 00:44:19,079
[SPEAKER_01] O milosrđu.

1465
00:44:21,219 --> 00:44:23,119
[SPEAKER_01] U privatnoj objavi dnevnika

1466
00:44:23,119 --> 00:44:24,659
[SPEAKER_01] svete Faustine Kovalske

1467
00:44:24,659 --> 00:44:26,460
[SPEAKER_01] Isus govori da oni svećenici

1468
00:44:26,460 --> 00:44:28,099
[SPEAKER_01] koji budu propovjedali

1469
00:44:28,099 --> 00:44:29,159
[SPEAKER_01] njegovo milosrđe,

1470
00:44:29,159 --> 00:44:32,679
[SPEAKER_01] da će Bog posebno pomazat njihove riječi.

1471
00:44:32,679 --> 00:44:35,440
[SPEAKER_01] i da će posebno doticat srca ljudi.

1472
00:44:35,440 --> 00:44:40,199
[SPEAKER_01] I meni je to došlo da kao lajk evangelizator

1473
00:44:40,199 --> 00:44:42,000
[SPEAKER_01] da otvorim srce za Božje milosrđe

1474
00:44:42,000 --> 00:44:44,199
[SPEAKER_01] i da dopustim Bogu da ih ljubi.

1475
00:44:44,900 --> 00:44:47,420
[SPEAKER_01] Jer ti ljudi su odbačeni, ranjeni.

1476
00:44:47,420 --> 00:44:49,719
[SPEAKER_01] A možda su odbačeni i od svoje obitelji.

1477
00:44:49,719 --> 00:44:51,760
